Carla Badillo Coronado posts a set of photos in her blog [_Mujer en Tierra
Firme [es]_](http://mujerentierrafirme.blogspot.com/2010/08/la-negritud-
luminosa-del-valle-del.html), showing the [Afro-Ecuadorian
](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afro-Ecuadorian_people)people of [Valle del
Chota](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valle_del_Chota).

